* On which platforms does IPL run?

The IPL compiler runs on any platform which has support for Ocaml and
LLVM with the Ocaml bindings.

The resulting programs are just LLVM assembly files and run on any
platform which is supported by LLVM.

* What license is IPL distributed under?

IPL is distributed under the Apache License version 2.0.

